Limitations

This research framework has several limitations:

Small stock universe
No transaction costs
No market capitalization weighting
No sector neutrality
No liquidity constraints
No institutional risk model

A production implementation would include:

Larger universe (S&P 500 / Russell 3000)
Transaction cost modeling
Factor exposure attribution
Risk factor decomposition
Portfolio optimization
Future Improvements

Possible extensions:

Add Value factor
Add Earnings Quality factor
Implement Fama-French regression
Add benchmark comparison
Add portfolio optimization
Add automated data pipeline
Conclusion

This project demonstrates a complete quantitative asset management workflow:

✓ Factor research
✓ Signal generation
✓ Portfolio construction
✓ Historical backtesting
✓ Risk analysis
✓ CAPM evaluation
✓ Interactive dashboard

The framework provides a foundation for further institutional-style factor investing research.
